# Coding Rules

Before writing or editing any Python or JavaScript file, READ
`docs/coding-rules.md` using the Read tool. Follow every rule in
that file. No exceptions.

Do NOT paraphrase or memorize the rules -- read the file every session
so you always have the latest version.
